query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `codonReadings` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  `userId` int NOT NULL,
  `carrierlockId` int NOT NULL,
  `readingText` text NOT NULL,
  `flaggedCodons` text NOT NULL,
  `sliScores` text NOT NULL,
  `activeFacets` text NOT NULL,
  `confidenceLevels` text NOT NULL,
  `microCorrection` text,
  `correctionFacet` enum('A', 'B', 'C', 'D'),
  `falsifier` text,
  `correctionCompleted` boolean NOT NULL DEFAULT false,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
);
